[I] Flatpak portal library

[T] libportal provides GIO-style async APIs for most Flatpak portals.
[T] You can find the documentation here.

[U] https://libportal.org/

[A] Matthias Clasen
[M] René Rebe <rene@exactco.de>

[C] extra/development
[F] CROSS

[E] add jinja2 markupsafe typogrify smartypants

[L] LGPL
[V] 0.10.0
[P] X -----5---9 109.300

[D] 0ba8fdf00931163cb4e586c379b464d49065e15d3eb960e635765b7f libportal-0.10.0.tar.xz https://github.com/flatpak/libportal/releases/download/0.10.0/

var_append mesonopt ' ' -Dtests=false
pkginstalled gtk+ || var_append mesonopt ' ' -Dbackend-gtk3=disabled
pkginstalled gtk || var_append mesonopt ' ' -Dbackend-gtk4=disabled
pkginstalled qt5base qt5x11extras || var_append mesonopt ' ' -Dbackend-qt5=disabled
pkginstalled qt6base || var_append mesonopt ' ' -Dbackend-qt6=disabled
pkginstalled gi-docgen || var_append mesonopt ' ' -Ddocs=false

var_append GCC_WRAPPER_APPEND ' ' -I$root/$(pkgprefix includedir libxcb)
